    // ---- Vista CALENDARIO (spec del fuente: celdas min-height 92, hoy en brand) ----

    private readonly record struct CalCell(DateTime Date, bool Valid, bool IsToday, List<(int ColIdx, ActivityCardDto Card)> Chips);

    /// <summary>
    /// Celdas del mes visible: arranca en lunes (offset del primer dia), 35 o 42 celdas.
    /// Los chips salen de las MISMAS tarjetas filtradas de las otras vistas, ubicadas
    /// por su DueDate (fecha local).
    /// </summary>
    private IEnumerable<CalCell> CalCells()
    {
        var byDay = ListRows()
            .Where(r => r.Card.DueDate is not null)
            .GroupBy(r => r.Card.DueDate!.Value.ToLocalTime().Date)
            .ToDictionary(g => g.Key, g => g.Select(r => (r.ColIdx, r.Card)).ToList());
        var today = DateTime.Today;
        var daysInMonth = DateTime.DaysInMonth(_calMonth.Year, _calMonth.Month);
        var offset = ((int)_calMonth.DayOfWeek + 6) % 7; // semana empieza en lunes
        var cells = (int)Math.Ceiling((offset + daysInMonth) / 7.0) * 7;
        for (var i = 0; i < cells; i++)
        {
            var day = i - offset + 1;
            if (day < 1 || day > daysInMonth)
            {
                yield return new CalCell(default, false, false, new List<(int, ActivityCardDto)>());
                continue;
            }
            var date = new DateTime(_calMonth.Year, _calMonth.Month, day);
            var chips = byDay.TryGetValue(date, out var list) ? list : new List<(int, ActivityCardDto)>();
            yield return new CalCell(date, true, date == today, chips);
        }
    }

    // ---- Vista GANTT (spec del fuente: ventana de 14 dias, barra por columna) ----

    private readonly record struct GanttDay(DateTime Date, bool Weekend);
    private readonly record struct GanttRow(ActivityCardDto Card, int ColIdx, string Left, string Width);

    private IEnumerable<GanttDay> GanttDays()
    {
        for (var i = 0; i < 14; i++)
        {
            var date = _ganttStart.AddDays(i);
            yield return new GanttDay(date, date.DayOfWeek is DayOfWeek.Saturday or DayOfWeek.Sunday);
        }
    }

    /// <summary>
    /// Filas del gantt: barra de StartDate a DueDate. Si falta StartDate usa CreatedAt;
    /// si falta DueDate usa StartDate + 1 dia. Se clampea a la ventana visible y las
    /// tareas totalmente fuera de rango se ocultan (spec de la ola).
    /// </summary>
    private IEnumerable<GanttRow> GanttRows()
    {
        foreach (var (_, colIdx, card) in ListRows())
        {
            var start = (card.StartDate ?? card.CreatedAt).ToLocalTime().Date;
            var end = card.DueDate?.ToLocalTime().Date ?? start.AddDays(1);
            if (end < start) { (start, end) = (end, start); }
            var s = (start - _ganttStart).Days;
            var e = (end - _ganttStart).Days;
            if (e < 0 || s > 13) { continue; } // fuera de la ventana visible
            var visStart = Math.Max(s, 0);
            var visEnd = Math.Min(e, 13);
            yield return new GanttRow(card, colIdx, GanttPct(visStart), GanttPct(visEnd - visStart + 1));
        }
    }

    /// <summary>Linea de HOY: left = ((dia - 0.5) / 14) * 100%, solo si cae en la ventana.</summary>
    private string? GanttTodayLeft()
    {
        var idx = (DateTime.Today - _ganttStart).Days;
        if (idx < 0 || idx > 13) { return null; }
        return ((idx + 0.5) / 14.0 * 100).ToString("0.00", System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture) + "%";
    }

    private static string GanttPct(int days)
        => (days / 14.0 * 100).ToString("0.00", System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture) + "%";

    private async Task QuickCreateAsync()
    {
        if (_detail is null || string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(_qcTitle)) { return; }
        _busy = true;
        _qcError = null;
        try
        {
            // ToUniversalTime: Npgsql solo acepta DateTimeOffset UTC en timestamptz
            // (mismo fix de Inicio.razor, sesion 9). Fin del dia LOCAL convertido a UTC.
            var due = _qcDue is DateTime d
                ? new DateTimeOffset(d.Date.AddHours(23).AddMinutes(59), DateTimeOffset.Now.Offset).ToUniversalTime()
                : (DateTimeOffset?)null;
            var request = new QuickCreateTaskRequest(
                BoardId: _detail.Id,
                ColumnId: _qcColumnId,
                Title: _qcTitle.Trim(),
                Description: string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(_qcDesc) ? null : _qcDesc.Trim(),
                Priority: _qcPriority,
                AssigneeTenantUserId: Guid.TryParse(_qcAssignee, out var assignee) ? assignee : null,
                DueDate: due,
                TagIds: _qcTagIds.Count == 0 ? null : _qcTagIds.ToList(),
                ActivityTypeId: Guid.TryParse(_qcTypeId, out var typeId) ? typeId : null,
                SubcategoriaId: Guid.TryParse(_qcSubId, out var subId) ? subId : null);
            var result = await BoardsSvc.QuickCreateTaskAsync(request, await ActorAsync(), await ActorNameAsync());
            if (!result.IsOk)
            {
                _qcError = result.Error;
                return;
            }
            _qcOpen = false;
            var created = result.Value!.Item;
            _toasts?.Success($"Actividad {created.Number} creada.");
            await BroadcastAsync(created.Id, created.Status);
            await LoadMembersAsync();
            await ReloadAsync();
        }
        finally
        {
            _busy = false;
        }
    }

